    "Id": "chassisdef_cockroach_CRH-2Br",
    "Name": "Cockroach",
    "Details": "The CRH-2Br is a common field refit of the original CRH-2B, replacing its single heat sinks with double heat sinks throughout. This simple upgrade allows the Cockroach's twin PPCs to fire more frequently without risking shutdown, meaningfully improving sustained combat performance while leaving the chassis's signature armor, reinforced actuators, and defensive systems entirely untouched.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Reinforced Structure</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.14</color></b>",
