  "StockRole": "Defensive Juggernaut",
  "YangsThoughts": "Designed in the waning years of the Star League to bolster SLDF garrisons amid mounting civil unrest, the Cockroach prioritized survivability above all else, trading offensive punch for unmatched resilience under fire. Following the Amaris Civil War, production blueprints scattered across the Inner Sphere, picked up intermittently by various manufacturers ever since. Now an uncommon but unsurprising sight in garrison forces of nearly every major faction, with scattered units even reaching Periphery militias.",
